-| SN | 1 bit [3] | 0/1 |
-| MD | 1 bit [4] | 0 |
-| CP | 1 bit [5] | 0 |
-| RFU | 2 bit [7:6] | 00 |
-| Length | 8 bit [15:8] | 13 |
